---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="mb-12">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-[#1f2937] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-4">
          <img id="avatar" src="/src/assets/img/propstfake.gif" alt="pfp" class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full border-2 border-[#D99058]" />
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#D99058]">propstgonz</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">~/about — probably overthinking something right now</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p id="typed-intro" class="text-sm text-cyan-300 terminal-cursor whitespace-pre-wrap"></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

<!-- Main -->
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-10">

    <!-- Logs -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#D99058] mb-3">[ logs ]</h2>
      <ul class="font-mono text-sm text-green-300 space-y-2">
        <li>[2025-07-28] updated this page and have started preparing to migrate it to Astro</li>
        <li>[2025-07-16] went back to Ubuntu for compatibility with some government programs</li>
        <li>[2025-07-2] fixed my mailserver</li>
      </ul>
      <div id="rotating-fish-container" class="ascii-art mt-4 text-center"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tools -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#D99058] mb-3">[ tools I kinda know how to use ]</h2>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
        <li class="bg-[#1f2937] p-2 border border-gray-600 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/src/assets/img/logo/html-logo.png" class="w-5 h-5" /> HTML / CSS
        </li>
        <li class="bg-[#1f2937] p-2 border border-gray-600 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/src/assets/img/logo/javascript-logo.png" class="w-5 h-5" /> JavaScript
        </li>
        <li class="bg-[#1f2937] p-2 border border-gray-600 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/src/assets/img/logo/postgix.png" class="w-5 h-5" /> Postfix & Dovecot
        </li>
        <li class="bg-[#1f2937] p-2 border border-gray-600 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/src/assets/img/logo/apache-logo.png" class="w-5 h-5" /> Nginx / Apache
        </li>
        <li class="bg-[#1f2937] p-2 border border-gray-600 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/src/assets/img/logo/docker-logo.png" class="w-5 h-5" /> Docker
        </li>
        <li class="bg-[#1f2937] p-2 border border-gray-600 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/src/assets/img/logo/Tux-logo.png" class="w-5 h-5" /> Linux
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#D99058] mb-3">[ a bit more human, I guess ]</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Life is not about seeking comfort or certainty, but about embracing the chaos within and around us. 
        True strength arises when we confront our deepest fears and contradictions, transforming them into fuel for our growth. In the struggle of becoming, we find our authentic selves—not in conformity, but in the bold creation of our own values. 
        To live fully is to say ‘yes’ to life’s challenges, to endure its suffering, and to rise beyond it, forging meaning where none existed before.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- My Stuff -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#D99058] mb-3">[ my stuff / where I put things ]</h2>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm">
        <li class="tool-button" onclick="location.href='/pc/'">🖥️ My computers</li>
        <li class="tool-button" data-vision-modal>🌌 My vision</li>
        <li class="tool-button" onclick="location.href='/faq/'">❓ FAQ</li>
        <li class="tool-button" onclick="location.href='/hub/'">🔗 My hub</li>
        <li class="tool-button" onclick="location.href='/clicker/'">📈 Clicker</li>
        <li class="tool-button" onclick="window.open('https://youtu.be/iik25wqIuFo?si=iAz2SpMPNyqpUVr_', '_blank')">😹 Funny kitty videos</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#D99058] mb-3">[ reach me / socials ]</h2>
      <div class="flex space-x-4 text-sm">
        <a href="https://github.com/propstgonz" target="_blank" class="hover:underline text-white">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://discord.com/users/1000141861333258393" target="_blank" class="hover:underline text-white">Discord</a>
        <a href="mailto:propstgonz@baronette.es" class="hover:underline text-white">Email</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-3">
        Also valid: <code>curl propstgonz.dev/contact (fake, I'll not buy another domain)</code>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="mt-16 text-center text-xs text-gray-500">
    <p>~ last update: 2025 — version 0.1.3-dev</p>
    <p>I'm becoming insane at this point...</p>
  </footer>

  <!-- Vision Modal -->
  <div id="visionModal" style="display:none;">
    <div class="close" data-close-vision-modal>X</div>
    <img src="img/happy18.png" alt="Vision" />
  </div>

  <!-- Scripts -->
  <script src="/src/assets/scripts/scripts.js"></script>
  <script src="/src/assets/scripts/change-avatar.js"></script>
</Layout>